{
  "stem": "17625.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 97.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I run over the, the road and within seconds came, came this-- the SS came with trucks and controlled everything.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, and [BACKROUND NOISE] I asked-- they-- the Crematorium 4 burnt the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Who burnt the crematorium?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The, the prisoners burned the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't get grenades.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said the SS used grenades.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If somebody went in to hide themselves, they threw in grenades.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But in no time, there was-- there was-- there was a avalanche of SS.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, and we had-- in Crematorium 5, there was a transport which we-- at work.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We just stopped for, for lunch and then come back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we came-- when, when, when the time came after lunch and we went back to work there was-- how many in there? 50 people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] They took the whole Crematorium 4, whoever was there-- whoever was there-- took him on the other side to us.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was this lawn.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like I call it a lawn-- before you got into the crematorium, was a little lawn.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the lawn was, was fenced around with, with, with little bushes you should-- you shouldn't be seen through.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, and, and sometimes when transports came, if there wasn't place inside in the mortuary to undress-- because there-- there wasn't a mortuary in the undressing room-- it was-- in 2 and 3 it was.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they told them to undress on, on this lawn.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they took in the whole kommando and laid them out on the lawn.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They went from one to one and shoot them in the neck.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And the whole night when this Crematorium 2 and 3 saw the fire from, from Crematorium 4, they start running off to the, the, the wires.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
